{"tid":1892422,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"(免費幫你設計屋企) 成本價幫你裝修","createTime":"2020-02-22T13:44:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-21T16:14:08.000Z","uid":27093,"like":161,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":76,"replies":[{"pid":"b7858222f0e1876392b1c2c0eb4154d24d10b280","tid":1892422,"uid":27093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T13:44:43.000Z","msg":"見好多人心思思想裝修 但出面閒閒地都收幾十萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屋企人本身做裝修 有uncle係做傢俬廠<br />\n自己屋企裝修緊 發現原來自己做係可以好平<br />\n所以心血來潮 想提供成本價 <strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">設計＋傢俬訂制＋裝修 一條龍服務</span></strong><br />\n幫下上左樓但無錢請室內設計/屋企住左好耐想裝修下既巴打絲打<br />\n有興趣可以搵我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n設計方面 <br />\n<br />\n只要有平面圖 就可以做到設計 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />（無圖都可以安排屋企人上門幫你度尺 不過就要另加收費）<br />\n會提供3D圖俾你睇 <br />\n都可以做埋3D全景漫遊 模擬你係屋企走黎走去 完全即視感 俾你睇到裝修完個樣 十分真實<br />\n不過呢個就比較複雜D 要花多小小時間 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />可以pm我拎link睇例子<br />\n<br />\n自己既設計例子：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HxDOf0n.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHxDOf0n.png&h=fb489d22&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Mwb4yM6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMwb4yM6.png&h=231e9b41&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GBXLidP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGBXLidP.png&h=4ef86e19&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n設計一開頭會收500定金，做貨時可以直接係貨款減去。<br />\n例如最後 傢俬＋材料＋裝修人工費 係3萬：<br />\n30000 - 500 ＝俾29500<br />\n<br />\n搵我設計完報個價就知<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">百分百成本價</span></strong>  <br />\n純粹係見個個為左屋企裝修 成日比人當水魚禁住搶錢<br />\n有小小能力可以做D野 等大家可以用合理既價錢 將屋企變成理想中既樣<br />\n<br />\n第一次搞 可能講得有甩漏<br />\n歡迎留言問我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9aa58cf74dd887dd89e5f2ed0a844e33d1071594","tid":1892422,"uid":27708,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T13:47:05.000Z","msg":"520尺兩房<br />\n唔搞廚廁 普通裝修<br />\n大概幾錢"},{"pid":"e9ee6a48de823424a6f6fbf504657f988d03bc49","tid":1892422,"uid":39438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T13:53:16.000Z","msg":"實尺400<br />\n廚房大約50尺<br />\n廁所40尺<br />\n換全屋地磚，廚廁牆地磚<br />\n油漆全屋<br />\n傢俬1張4尺床，1個4尺衣櫃，一個3尺玄關櫃<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n幾錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"408ddf57167ee71a80186330bf071148a5f27f75","tid":1892422,"uid":40908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T13:53:21.000Z","msg":"有無tg"},{"pid":"ac9e5d00775d2f19aae1a44d8b36e597a778740f","tid":1892422,"uid":9151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T13:56:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea1ec65d895deb05e9bb98b49219b001dcc58ef0","tid":1892422,"uid":164932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T13:56:26.000Z","msg":"有冇公司<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63413895420df7dc467ac5215dd220b90bc55c39","tid":1892422,"uid":48974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T13:56:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06843bd3bd46e24ab1b781f26c788d56ad6cbe44","tid":1892422,"uid":227275,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T13:57:54.000Z","msg":"只買傢俬可以?<br />\n成本價好吸引"},{"pid":"5bc9bf1be14056f244074f8ca5b8cd70d7f11f86","tid":1892422,"uid":52332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T13:59:39.000Z","msg":"實尺457 兩房<br />\n點聯絡巴打好 PM你?"},{"pid":"4