設計＋傢俬訂制＋裝修 一條龍服務</span></strong><br />\n幫下上左樓但無錢請室內設計/屋企住左好耐想裝修下既巴打絲打<br />\n有興趣可以搵我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n設計方面 <br />\n<br />\n只要有平面圖 就可以做到設計 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />（無圖都可以安排屋企人上門幫你度尺 不過就要另加收費）<br />\n會提供3D圖俾你睇 <br />\n都可以做埋3D全景漫遊 模擬你係屋企走黎走去 完全即視感 俾你睇到裝修完個樣 十分真實<br />\n不過呢個就比較複雜D 要花多小小時間 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />可以pm我拎link睇例子<br />\n<br />\n自己既設計例子：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HxDOf0n.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHxDOf0n.png&h=fb489d22&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Mwb4yM6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMwb4yM6.png&h=231e9b41&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GBXLidP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGBXLidP.png&h=4ef86e19&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n設計一開頭會收500定金，做貨時可以直接係貨款減去。<br />\n例如最後 傢俬＋材料＋裝修人工費 係3萬：<br />\n30000 - 500 ＝俾29500<br />\n<br />\n搵我設計完報個價就知<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">百分百成本價</span></strong>  <br />\n純粹係見個個為左屋企裝修 成日比人當水魚禁住搶錢<br />\n有小小能力可以做D野 等大家可以用合理既價錢 將屋企變成理想中既樣<br />\n<br />\n第一次搞 可能講得有甩漏<br />\n歡迎留言問我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T12:12:37.000Z","msg":"想請問會唔會有設計圖可以參考下？"},{"pid":"69fdd2811262a9865bc3d9af4e6ccd4863c86176","tid":1892422,"uid":207476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T19:10:00.000Z","msg":"留名<br />\n想要設計圖"},{"pid":"585a26dcb1f3fae2f149279d8a67dd1641c3e836","tid":1892422,"uid":117947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T00:50:34.000Z","msg":"1300呎大執要預幾錢"},{"pid":"c642c2794b4ba636d07a49bb20eb70c507249f42","tid":1892422,"uid":345391,"like":0,